string.name: privacy_content
string.Data: "Welcome to Wallpaper Carousel. This app provides customized wallpaper browsing services. Wallpaper Carousel needs to collect necessary personal information to provide you with these services. You can learn how we handle the information we collect in our Privacy Policy and User Agreement. You can always change the related settings in the \"Privacy Policy\" section of the app. If you don't agree to such terms and conditions, select \"Turn off Wallpaper Carousel\". By selecting \"Agree\", you're agreeing to our Privacy Policy and turning on Wallpaper Carousel."
